title: Senior Project in Computing Arts II
description: Continuation of MUS 160A or VIS 160A. Completion and presentation of independent projects along with documentation. Two production-course limitation. Renumbered from ICAM 160B. Students may receive credit for only one of the following: MUS 160B, VIS 160B, ICAM 160B. Prerequisites: MUS 160A or VIS 160A. Open to music and ICAM majors only. Department stamp required.
